sentences: Irina Igorevna Nusinova (Russian: Ирина Игоревна Нусинова; born 17 September 1982), better known by her stage name Irson Kudikova (Russian: Ирсон Кудикова), is a Russian pop singer, model, saxophonist, music producer, and actress.
In 2005, Kudikova had a photo shoot for Maxim magazine.
Early years =
Kudikova was born on 17 September 1982 in Moscow.
In 2004, Kudikova was a participant in the teleproject "Alla Pugacheva's Star Factory-5".

sentences: In 2010, Kudikova founded her own company "Irson Production", allowing her to take the independent route for her career.
In 2011, Kudikova recorded a duet with American rapper Warren G called "Innocent".
Kudikova currently owns the jewelry company "Golden heart" and her personal entertainment company "Irson Productions".
